{
  "text": "This is just right (3) in [CITATION_1] without the distribution of Y r for r \u2208 [s, t]. So, in the case Definition 2.11 is Definition 2.1 in [CITATION_2] without the distribution of Y r for r \u2208 [s, t].",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "207853284",
